## Permission Model

Based on certificate groups:

| Group | Capabilities |
|-------|--------------|
| `admin` | Full access, mesh config, execution routing |
| `developer` | Read/write entities, request executions |
| `readonly` | Read entities only |

```typescript
class SudocodeMeshService {
  private checkPermission(peer: PeerInfo, action: string): boolean {
    switch (action) {
      case 'write':
        return peer.groups.some(g => ['admin', 'developer'].includes(g))
      case 'execute':
        return peer.groups.some(g => ['admin', 'developer'].includes(g))
      case 'read':
        return true  // All groups can read
      default:
        return false
    }
  }
}
```

